docs {
  **Step 32 — Patient-wise report.** Paginated, enriched collection rows (patient,
  order, charges, sample/collection counts). Accepts the same filters as the list
  endpoint: `search`, `status`, `phlebotomistId`, `dateFrom`, `dateTo`, `page`,
  `limit`, `branchId`.
}
